I"<p>Scenius is the term given to a small collective of ambitious individuals working in a cutting-edge field who somehow manage to come up with surprisingly many great ideas. The notion of scenius highlights the value of <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/feynman-cluster-infuses-learning-by-teaching-with-social-structure">social structure in knowledge work</a> and the value of <a class="internal-link" href="/secondbrain/diversity-in-problem-solving-sidesteps-ideological-debt">diversity in problem solving</a>.</p>
